criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  previously untreated participants with cluster of differentiation 20 (CD20) positive
             B-cell chronic lymphocytic leukemia;

          -  participants with progressive Binet stage B, or C requiring therapy according to
             National Cancer Institute (NCI) criteria;

          -  Eastern Cooperative Oncology Group (ECOG) performance status <=2.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  previous treatment for Chronic Lymphocytic Leukaemia (CLL);

          -  known concomitant hematological malignancy;

          -  transformation to aggressive B-cell malignancy;

          -  history of severe cardiac disease;

          -  known hypersensitivity or anaphylactic reactions to murine antibodies.
